stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> WaitingInput
  WaitingInput --> ModelTurn: user goal
  ModelTurn --> ToolTurn: tool intent
  ModelTurn --> Final: final answer
  ToolTurn --> Observe: success
  ToolTurn --> Recover: error
  Observe --> ModelTurn: append observation
  Recover --> ModelTurn: retry or explain
  Recover --> Failed: unrecoverable
  ModelTurn --> Paused: budget or interrupt
  ToolTurn --> Paused: timeout or interrupt
  Paused --> ModelTurn: resume
  Final --> [*]
  Failed --> [*]

  ModelTurn:::hot
  Recover:::hot
  Paused:::hot

  classDef hot fill:#fff3b0,stroke:#111,stroke-width:2px,color:#111;
